text: Chris Lake is a DJ/producer who first became recognized for his remixes of The Prodigy's Climbatize, Leftfield's Phat Planet, and The Eurythmics Sweet Dreams. Since then, he has released many singles on labels such as Lost Language and 3 Beat Breaks. He also founded his own label, Cuba Recordings.
